Class ImportMP3

java.lang.Object
  ImportMP3

public class ImportMP3
extends Object

Author:
Cheng Peng This class is to help the MusicLibrary class to import real mp3 files via jAudioTagger library. Go to http://www.jthink.net/jaudiotagger/ for more details.
